CONCHO SAND & GRAVEL COMPANY, Inc., v. UNITED STATES of America. No. 3363. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. June 26, 1946. A. E. Pearson, of Oklahoma City, Old., and Hamilton & Kane, of Pawhuska, Old., for cross-appellant. Charles E. Dierker, U. S. Atty., and Robert E. Shelton, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of Oklahoma City, Old., for cross-appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, Circuit Judge, and SYMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Cross-appeal docketed and dismissed pursuant to stipulation.
